reviewText: Great! Introductory DVD for a toddler!!

This is a must have DVD if you have babies at home. My 17 month old daughter loves it and the best thing is she's learning all the time. I'm very glad with this product because it's entertaining as well as educational for young children

I've used tons of DVD's to help teach my son to speak. By far the best! The Parrot character is the friendliest, cutest thing and my son just loves mimicking him. A great purchase for babies who are figuring their words out!

My grandson loves VocabuLarry
Our twins love this!  It is just Larry, which is what we wanted, instead of having all the other characters/shows with it.

We love Baby First TV in our home...especially VocabuLarry!  Our 2 year old is autistic and Larry( or "Arry" as he calls him) is the first stuffed animal our son could identify and go get when you asked him to!  That has happened in the last six weeks and is a very very big deal....So Larry now goes with us everywhere and we watch Larry on all our trips...even just to the grocery store!  I love hearing my lil mans voice after 27 months trying to repeat Larry!  Thank You Baby First tv
